-- Spot Gold Declines 0.5% in Early Asian Trade; Futures Advance
-- B y   P h o e b e   S e d g m a n
-- 2012-05-28T22:19:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-28/spot-gold-declines-0-5-in-early-asian-trade-futures-advance.html
Gold for immediate delivery declined
0.5 percent to $1,573.90 an ounce at 8:13 a.m. in  Melbourne ,
while August-delivery bullion advanced 0.3 percent to $1,575.50.
Silver for July delivery was little changed at $28.385 an ounce.  To contact the reporter on this story:
